# Cursor Rules for PDF Processing Project

## Project Overview
This is a PDF processing project using Python with pdfplumber, pypdf, and other libraries.

## Code Style
- Use Python type hints where possible
- Write docstrings for functions
- Follow PEP 8 style guide
- Use meaningful variable names in both English and Persian contexts

## Key Dependencies
- pdfplumber: For text extraction from PDFs
- pypdf: For PDF manipulation
- cryptography: For encryption support

## Project Structure
- Main entry point: robust_pdf_to_json.py
- Virtual environment: pdf_venv/
- Configuration: .gitignore for excluding venv

## Background Agent Rules
- Automatically fetch from origin/main
- Monitor changes in PDF processing scripts
- Suggest improvements for text extraction
- Help maintain code quality and performance
